{'hash': '5cf9920afe6001336ba13f62de903719d4a804a9', 'query': 'SELECT T3.name, SUM(T1.balance) + SUM(T2.balance) FROM SAVINGS AS T1 JOIN CHECKING AS T2 ON T1.custid = T2.custid JOIN ACCOUNTS AS T3 ON T1.custid = T3.custid WHERE T3.custid BETWEEN 1 AND 100 OR T1.balance > 1000 OR T2.balance > 1000 GROUP BY T3.name', 'template': 'SELECT #COLUMN#, SUM(#COLUMN#) + SUM(#COLUMN#) FROM #TABLE# JOIN #TABLE# ON #COLUMN# = #COLUMN# JOIN #TABLE# ON #COLUMN# = #COLUMN# WHERE #COLUMN# BETWEEN #VALUE# AND #VALUE# OR #COLUMN# > #VALUE# OR #COLUMN# > #VALUE# GROUP BY #COLUMN#'}
